{"attribution":"Occupational Safety and Health Administration, On-Site Consultation for Small Business, OSHA 4230-05 2023, Chinese Simplified; no OSHA or U.S. Department of Labor endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"每个已避免的工伤节省大约 8500美元，一个已避免的工人赔偿诉求可以让您的保险率，以及受伤致病率保持在低水平，而这可以让您在其他公司选择可靠的业务合作伙伴时更加具有吸引力。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"工地的有效安全与健康项目会让您的工人更好地，更有效率地工作，提高生产率，并确保产品质量。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"工人更倾向于留在一个关注他们健康的公司。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"参加OSHA现场咨询项目是一种回馈工人的方式。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"工人安全是经营一个成功企业的必要条件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"安全咨询可以帮助企业去提问和思考必要的问题，来创建一个安全的工作环境。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"小型企业可能没有预算来雇佣一个安全专家，但是这个项目可以免费提供相似的建议。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"即使您的企业还没有经历任何与工作相关的伤亡事件，但是评估工作环境的安全隐患是很重要的。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"目标是在现在以及未来去降低工人受伤或致疾的可能性。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"告诉我们您的安全顾虑 — 咨询会帮您找出解决方案联系当地现场咨询办公室，预约一次咨询访问。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"您的企业唯一义务是，在合理的时间内，纠正不安全，不健康的工作条件。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"顾问会与管理层和工人代表会面，谈论顾问的职责和雇主的义务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"雇主，工人代表，以及顾问，三者协同详谈该企业，并找出现有的和潜在的安全隐患。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"顾问可以审阅您的安全与健康管理项目，甚至可以免费为您提供职业健康样本。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-015","input":"在结束会议上，顾问会和您，以及工人代表，一起详细查看所找出的安全隐患。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-016","input":"您会得知需要提高哪些方面，您所做的正确举动，成本方面的考虑，以及如何持续进步。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-017","input":"顾问离开后，您会收到一份详细的纸质版咨询报告总结，确认所需纠正之处。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-018","input":"若一个情况被定义为“严重”的安全隐患，顾问会帮您开展一个计划，在合理的时间框架内，纠正安全隐患，并同时保护您的工人。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-019","input":"顾问是谁? 州机关和大学都咨询安全与工业卫生专家。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-020","input":"他们的专业背景，结合OSHA 的培训，使他们成为了理想选择，来帮助您找到有安全与健康隐患之处，不管是在您所有的设备中，还是在部分设备中。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-021","input":"顾问会帮您找出您企业中的安全与健康需求，并预约一个对您方便的日期。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1/sentence-022","input":"求职者更看好一个拥有强大安全记录的潜在雇主。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/OSHA4230.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"document"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"osha-small-business-consultation-simplified-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted complete Simplified Chinese sentences from the checksum-pinned OSHA PDF, excluded URLs, phone instructions, page furniture, images, logos, attributed third-party testimonials, and other third-party content, and added input-only provenance; no expected text or converter output was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"document":22},"eligible_pending_review":22,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":22},"upstream_revision":"OSHA 4230-05 2023, On-Site Consultation for Small Business, Chinese Simplified; retrieved PDF SHA-256: cdcedd100ce05013968026e640079d7044deb913178496424f71b89481a5567e","version":1}
